Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does every single rental car we get break down, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since we're in the middle of the mountains, we can't even use our cell phones!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we have no choice but to wait here until the fog clears up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Don't smoke in such a narrow space, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it fine if I open the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez... What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, could it be that you're scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, there could be a mountain spirit looking at us through the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you! I can't hear you! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, what a chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could there be a side street in the middle of the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Uncle, that means that the car just now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Cigar Case of Good Fortune\NPart 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The billboard back there said there's a company development facility up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way anyone would be there this late at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car we saw earlier had to have been some robbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go ahead of you guys and check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, but be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still a little warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a cute car!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner of such a cute car can't be a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like there are other cars here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one is warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably the car we saw heading here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car is warm, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, people must still be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kuron Health Appliances Company", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never heard of 'em before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two, be on your best behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not late enough for people to be sleeping yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our car just broke down nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were stuck in this fog and thought you might be able to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please ask someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least let us use your phone, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is that jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear that when I die, my ghost will come back to haunt you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get back to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, do come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! It's really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our company training facility, so it's rare for people to be here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, there's the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'll make a quick call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will we do if they're corporate spies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not the least bit suspicious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's to be expected from Development Team 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've sure got some guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all this yapping about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am, by no means, a suspicious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Mouri Kogoro, a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the famous sleeping detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my daughter, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this little guy is Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well. It's a Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Umetani, the president of Kuron Health Appliances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, please take as much time as you need for your phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should let Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} try them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're having a competition to see which development team can design the most relaxing chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy if you could try them as an end-user and give me your opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so embarrassing.!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've been in a such a great massage chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It even gets to all the stiff points in my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We took the softness of natural leather and combined it with the durability of artificial leather...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To provide the ultimate comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected from Development Department 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good job, Nakano!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, President...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That "ultimate comfort leather" he's\Nso proud of is an Italian-made product.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the internal mechanisms are made from high-quality silicone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The costs it would take to mass-produce it are way too high, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself, Nakano!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basic parts like the roller are manufactured on the same production line as our older models...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So to make it more durable, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't need durability!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even if we take a loss at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be building up a base of satisfied customers, and someday, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Someday" isn't good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want profits now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't continue improving our products...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our customers will leave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next chair is called the Ecstasy 1, and was produced by Development Department 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This product is aimed at our younger customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seat is protected by a cover, which will make it fit in with our clients' interiors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it will come in seven different color variations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The back of the chair can be inclined up to 180 degrees...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if it's placed in your living room, it can also be converted into a sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainlytjvould be suitable for a young person's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To'dperate it, you can use the remote control, which is in the pocket on the side of the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first setting is a full-body massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you getting sleepy, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell is it doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this version is intended for young people, it may be a bit too strong for you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please try it again on the weak "resting mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of feeling relaxing, it felt like it was ripping my body apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasahara! That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next! Hiramatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... What is this supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it equipment to battle monsters or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, my son had an action figure that looked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true. You look like a robot from an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now... Please give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does it know exactly where I want to be massaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its built-in micro sensors locate\Nthe stiffest parts of your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And automatically adjusts its strength to your needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That looks like a amazing machine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it going to be really expensive to mass-produce?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the only new feature is the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other parts are the same as the ones we used in older models.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thinkjthat this design costs less than half of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that.1...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we heavily promote this feature, we'll be able to sell it for a very high price, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which machine should I market to the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll look over the details one more time, and be back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, take as much time as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still can't decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This just feels so good, I could fall asleep right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! You're bothering,everyone in their work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks he's already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today was a fast unveiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the rumors about your top-secret project were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wasn't Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the perfect person to test it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president doesn't even need to consider anything, he's giving himself some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be that the rumors about cutting one of the Development Departments are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably in there now, thinking about which Development Department he'll shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, aboutyour seat, Kasahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone wanted to sit in it without turning it on, wouldn't it make them stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's as hard as a rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please keep working well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to your work that people can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! Speaking of young people, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you test the chairs too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be playing around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are knives, and they're very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was wondering if they were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president is a collector>of famous knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're'often a topic of conservation with our clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even has some decorating our-company office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to market the Aimuzu chair, designed by Development Department 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to merge Departments 1 and 2 into a single department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone is dismissed, except you Hiramatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll talk later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please relax in the lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I'm finished with this business discussion, why don't you tell me some your stories over a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, they won't be able to bring a tow truck out here until the fog clears up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you're glad to hear that, aren't you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because now you can have that drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, would you like to have a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll help you make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to go to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The restrooms are across from\Nthe room we came out of earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go down the hall, and it's the second door on the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please annul the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can no longer bear to work under your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you take me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I really look like a man who's generous enough to agree with that request?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I took some precautionary measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With them, you'll be dying to agree with me in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The result is certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sure are taking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For all we know, the president's in there threatening him again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And is forcing him to sign another one of those vile contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Vile contracts?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what does "Annul a contract" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not something a kid needs to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy, did Hiramatsu say that to the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Hiramatsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wants to resign?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, does that mean thatyyou're all contract employees?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever the president finds some talented development company...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He uses all his strength, and easily coerces them into signing a long-term contract with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you say "all his strength" you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the type of man the president is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's even a black belt in karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, even if he doesn't use his brute strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can usually intimidate weak-minded people into signing on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Kasahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I were hired by the former company president...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we've never experienced that treatment ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all the other Development Department workers have been "trained" in this Internship Dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since this place is tax-exempt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He uses company money to buy more knives for his hobby, presents for women...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or whatever the hell else he may want to to buy on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the receipts up to today show that it's just like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird... It sounds like a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Hiramatsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where he's going...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the window over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's open...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, wait! Don't touch anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umetani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, call an ambulance and the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Ran's taking care of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,go after Hiromatsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take this car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I have the keys for it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the president's car, but since I'm driving him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, one of the tires is flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it the same for the other cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car also has a flat tire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beingdn the middle of the mountains, rather than waiting for the ambulance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would have been faster to drive him to the hospital ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umetani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President, please hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The knife fell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The knife got stuck in this cigar case!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, doesn't that mean that cigar case saved his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umetani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what the heck happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiramatsu suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiramatsu suddenly... with a knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the accident occurred, the fog was very thick...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with the sharp curve here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably lost control during his escape and plummeted to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the most likely scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have panicked over some other car, because no one was chasing after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he didn't have a need to flee the scene at such high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was someone who could think rationally like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have flown into a rage and stabbed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're as sharp as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since the victim sustained only minor injuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can ask him what happened back then, and easily find the motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this mirror for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a corner mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This whole plot of land was bought by the company, so this is a private road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it looks like nobody's there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, see that company billboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its seclusion makes people think it's a welfare facility, or even a boarding-house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This big rock makes it very dangerous for a driver when they're leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it obstructs the driver's field of vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? There's a sharp curve at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've installed similar curve mirrors on the public road, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of road maintenance in this area, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I simply requested that they install a corner mirror on their private road.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mirrorjs direction changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They installed an extra-large one, but it looks like it was blown by the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was properly positioned this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should put it in place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that could be the cause of this accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Uncle Mouri asked that you have the brakes of the victim's car checked immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brakes might have gone out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let the others know now, so hold on aisecond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever it was, we're heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, stop playing around all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're holding everyone up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down,<Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Inspector Yokomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about what Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.asked us earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the victim's car was completely drained.of brake fluid—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, we still haven't figured out whether it accidentally fell off during the car's impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or whether someone purposely removed it beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the tube connecting the brake fluid chamber has been completely removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brakes failed because there wasn't any brake fluid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes it completely natural that an accident would occur on this narrowly winding mountain road.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are just too many strange things aboUtythis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we have a man who stabbed someone out of rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And punctured other cars' tires so no one would be able to pursue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, he loses control of his steering wheel during his escape, and crashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curve mirror that had its direction changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brake tluid that had been drained...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something... There's definitely something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rope, a stun gun and a will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does it say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:23:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! What the hell does this'mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, call Inspector Yokomizo and the others back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an ingeniously disguised murder!
